<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:08:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联合国：工人在全球收入中所占份额急剧下降</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/workers-see-dramatic-fall-in-share-of-global-income-un/articleshow/113059967.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113059967.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国国际劳工组织表示，自2004年以来，全球劳动收入份额下降了1.6%，导致每年工人短缺2.4万亿美元。这种下降因 Covid-19 大流行而加剧，凸显了不平等现象的加剧，并强调需要制定政策来确保公平的经济分配。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:36:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/workers-see-dramatic-fall-in-share-of-global-income-un/articleshow/113059967.cms</guid></item><item><title>计划于五月进行世界巡游的船舶在贝尔法斯特滞留了三个月</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ship-scheduled-for-world-cruise-in-may-has-been-stranded-in-belfast-for-past-three-months/articleshow/113049474.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113049474.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;大约 200 名乘客滞留在贝尔法斯特，等待 Villa Vie Residences 的奥德赛 (Odyssey) 启航，开始为期三年的环球航行。这艘船于 1993 年建造，自 2020 年起停产，需要对其舵轴、钢结构和发动机进行维修。乘客可以在船上度过一天，但必须每天晚上离开。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ship-scheduled-for-world-cruise-in-may-has-been-stranded-in-belfast-for-past-three-months/articleshow/113049474.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普声称，“如果当选，将公布不明飞行物录像和杰弗里·爱泼斯坦的文件”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/will-release-ufo-footage-jeffrey-epsteins-documents-if-elected-trump-claims/articleshow/113054792.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113054792.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普承诺，如果赢得总统选举，他将公布不明飞行物录像和杰弗里·爱泼斯坦的文件。他还打算就约翰·F·肯尼迪遇刺事件成立一个委员会，并在任期初期公开相关文件。特朗普澄清说，尽管他们相识，但他与爱泼斯坦没有任何关系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:17:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/will-release-ufo-footage-jeffrey-epsteins-documents-if-elected-trump-claims/articleshow/113054792.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗因 Instagram 帖子支持 LGBTQIA+ 权利而召见澳大利亚大使</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/iran-summons-australian-ambassador-over-instagram-post-supporting-lgbtqia-rights/articleshow/113052673.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113052673.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚驻德黑兰大使馆在 Instagram 上发布了庆祝 LGBTQIA+ 青年“穿紫色日”的帖子后，伊朗召见了澳大利亚大使。伊朗批评该帖子宣扬同性恋并违背伊斯兰传统，而澳大利亚则捍卫其人权立场。该帖子仍可在大使馆的 Instagram 页面上查看。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:36:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/iran-summons-australian-ambassador-over-instagram-post-supporting-lgbtqia-rights/articleshow/113052673.cms</guid></item><item><title>“不要忽视我们”：哈马斯发布被杀以色列人质呼救的视频</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/do-not-neglect-us-hamas-releases-video-of-slain-israeli-hostage-calling-for-help/articleshow/113054612.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113054612.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯发布了一段视频，显示奥里·达尼诺(Ori Danino)，他是在拉法被处决的六名人质之一。在视频中，达尼诺描述了恶劣的生活条件，并批评以色列领导层的救援尝试失败。他敦促以色列人继续努力拯救人质，并最后恳求“以色列人民：不要忽视我们。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 07:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/do-not-neglect-us-hamas-releases-video-of-slain-israeli-hostage-calling-for-help/articleshow/113054612.cms</guid></item><item><title>长岛男子被女友嫉妒的前夫杀害，葬礼上被铭记为“英雄”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/long-island-man-killed-by-girlfriends-jealous-ex-husband-remembered-as-hero-at-funeral/articleshow/113047008.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047008.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 53 岁的长岛居民肯尼思·波尔曼 (Kenneth Pohlman) 是三个孩子的父亲，他在圣詹姆斯保护女友免受前夫伤害时被枪杀，后被安葬。哀悼者缅怀他作为父亲和体育爱好者的奉献精神。丹尼尔·科波拉曾对前妻凯莉·科波拉表现出虐待行为，现已被捕并承认杀人。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/long-island-man-killed-by-girlfriends-jealous-ex-husband-remembered-as-hero-at-funeral/articleshow/113047008.cms</guid></item><item><title>亨利是谁？世界上最年长的鳄鱼，与六位伴侣共产下 10,000 个孩子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/who-is-henry-worlds-oldest-crocodile-who-has-fathered-10000-babies-with-six-partners/articleshow/113047554.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047554.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;亨利是一条重 700 公斤、长 16 英尺的巨型尼罗河鳄鱼，现已正式成为世界上最年长的鳄鱼，享年 123 岁。它居住在南非鳄鱼世界保护中心，已生育了 10,000 多个后代。 1903 年，亨利因捕食儿童而在博茨瓦纳被捕，如今他的生活已经远离了他的暴力过去。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/who-is-henry-worlds-oldest-crocodile-who-has-fathered-10000-babies-with-six-partners/articleshow/113047554.cms</guid></item><item><title>官员称，数千罗兴亚人因缅甸暴力事件逃往孟加拉国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/thousands-of-rohingya-flee-to-bangladesh-from-violence-in-myanmar-official-says/articleshow/113052570.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113052570.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近，约有 8,000 名罗兴亚穆斯林越境进入孟加拉国，逃离缅甸若开邦不断升级的暴力局势。孟加拉国官员报告说，该国难民负担已经过重，无法容纳更多难民。政府计划就这场危机进行紧急讨论，并敦促国际社会采取行动，制止缅甸持续发生的暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/thousands-of-rohingya-flee-to-bangladesh-from-violence-in-myanmar-official-says/articleshow/113052570.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国极右翼德国选择党的崛起引发了集中营所在地的恐惧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/rise-of-germanys-far-right-afd-stokes-fears-at-concentration-camp-site/articleshow/113052167.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113052167.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;负责监督德国布痕瓦尔德集中营纪念馆的历史学家对极右翼选择党在图林根州选举中获胜后不断上升的威胁感到震惊。他预计反移民情绪将会增加，纪念馆的预算可能会被削减，该纪念馆纪念了超过 56,000 名纳粹罪行的受害者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/rise-of-germanys-far-right-afd-stokes-fears-at-concentration-camp-site/articleshow/113052167.cms</guid></item><item><title>空中交通管制员被发现睡着后，澳大利亚政府将制定新规定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-government-to-enact-new-regulations-after-air-traffic-controller-found-asleep/articleshow/113051080.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113051080.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2022 年 12 月 9 日，一名空中交通管制员被发现在布里斯班空中交通服务中心值班期间打瞌睡，澳大利亚运输安全局颁布了新规定。一项调查揭示了疲劳管理实践中的重大问题。作为回应，澳大利亚航空服务公司增加了人员配备并更新了疲劳评估工具，以防止再次发生此类事件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-government-to-enact-new-regulations-after-air-traffic-controller-found-asleep/articleshow/113051080.cms</guid></item><item><title>复仇心切的泰国跨性别女人十多年来诈骗了 70 多名日本男人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vengeful-thai-trans-woman-scams-over-70-japanese-men-for-over-a-decade/articleshow/113049690.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113049690.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名名叫艾米的泰国变性女子在13年时间里诈骗了70多名日本男子近3000万泰铢。被日本男友抛弃后，她开始向日本男人复仇。她冒充来自台湾或香港的游客来博取同情并操纵男人。她于8月4日在曼谷被捕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vengeful-thai-trans-woman-scams-over-70-japanese-men-for-over-a-decade/articleshow/113049690.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦政府禁止公务员未经许可使用社交媒体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-government-bars-public-servants-from-using-social-media-without-permission/articleshow/113050217.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113050217.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦政府已限制所有政府雇员未经事先许可使用社交媒体，以防止官方信息泄露。禁止员工分享可能影响政府声誉、政策或国家主权的意见或文件。机构必须监控社交媒体是否存在任何令人反感的内容。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-government-bars-public-servants-from-using-social-media-without-permission/articleshow/113050217.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈里王子会重返王室职责吗？苏塞克斯公爵澄清</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/is-prince-harry-returning-to-royal-duties-duke-of-sussex-clarifies/articleshow/113049040.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113049040.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈里王子似乎对恢复王室职责不感兴趣，并与好朋友定居在加利福尼亚州。尽管有传言称他会回国，但由于他目前在美国的处境并不理想，他还是向老熟人寻求建议。他计划在联合国大会高级别周期间前往纽约进行慈善工作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:16:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/is-prince-harry-returning-to-royal-duties-duke-of-sussex-clarifies/articleshow/113049040.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普在修订后的 2020 年选举起诉书指控中不认罪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-to-plead-not-guilty-in-revised-2020-election-indictment-charges/articleshow/113048214.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113048214.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普将对指控他试图推翻 2020 年选举失败的刑事指控表示无罪。他的法律团队提交了一份文件，允许他们代表他进行抗辩。尽管起诉书有所修改，但指控保持不变，法庭听证会定于周四进行。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:11:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-to-plead-not-guilty-in-revised-2020-election-indictment-charges/articleshow/113048214.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜据称因洪水失败而处决了30名政府官员</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-kim-jong-un-allegedly-executes-30-government-officials-for-flood-failures/articleshow/113048212.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113048212.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩已处决了至少 30 名官员，因为他们未能阻止造成数千人死亡的毁灭性夏季洪水。朝鲜中央通讯社证实了金正恩严惩的命令。尽管邻国提出提供援助，但朝鲜拒绝提供援助。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:40:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-kim-jong-un-allegedly-executes-30-government-officials-for-flood-failures/articleshow/113048212.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国不断撞击菲律宾船只以及其走向</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-china-keeps-ramming-philippine-ships-and-where-thats-headed/articleshow/113047748.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047748.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着中国海警与菲律宾船只发生冲突，南海紧张局势升级。这场以萨宾娜浅滩为中心的冲突引起了全球关注，并涉及多个亚洲国家。美国受与菲律宾的防务条约约束，可能会被拖入与中国的直接冲突。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 02:58:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-china-keeps-ramming-philippine-ships-and-where-thats-headed/articleshow/113047748.cms</guid></item><item><title>“浪费开支”：哈里王子和梅根·马克尔的哥伦比亚之旅费用揭晓</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/wasteful-spending-prince-harry-meghan-markles-colombia-tour-cost-revealed/articleshow/113047943.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047943.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈里王子和梅根·马克尔对哥伦比亚为期四天的访问花费了该国近 45,000 英镑，用于安全和内部交通。这对夫妇自己支付了机票和住宿费用。总支出为 244,245,305 科拉（44,725.14 英镑），涵盖了此次旅行的各个方面，包括整个旅行期间的安全和内部交通。总成本涵盖8月12日至19日的八天时间。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/wasteful-spending-prince-harry-meghan-markles-colombia-tour-cost-revealed/articleshow/113047943.cms</guid></item><item><title>女子点燃两场野火与消防员调情</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/mad-mad-world/woman-starts-two-wildfires-to-flirt-with-firefighters-greece-tripoli/articleshow/113047541.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047541.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;希腊的黎波里的一名女子因故意纵火两起并与消防员调情而被定罪。她被判处三年缓刑和 1,000 欧元罚款。鉴于 2024 年 8 月希腊爆发严重山火，消防部门迅速控制了火势，这一点至关重要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 02:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/mad-mad-world/woman-starts-two-wildfires-to-flirt-with-firefighters-greece-tripoli/articleshow/113047541.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦女教师因拒绝求婚被枪杀</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/female-teacher-shot-dead-in-pakistan-for-refusing-marriage-proposal/articleshow/113047878.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047878.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在开伯尔-普赫图赫瓦省布内尔，一名 40 岁的女教师在拒绝求婚后在父亲面前被枪杀。嫌疑人逃跑了。这一悲惨事件突显了巴基斯坦犯罪率上升的趋势，包括最近发生的“荣誉”杀人事件，其中妇女因违背家人意愿结婚而被谋杀。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 02:51:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/female-teacher-shot-dead-in-pakistan-for-refusing-marriage-proposal/articleshow/113047878.cms</guid></item><item><title>“对他们一无所知”：唐纳德·特朗普的侄子弗雷德·特朗普因军事不尊重而抨击叔叔</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/doesnt-give-a-st-about-them-donald-trumps-nephew-fred-trump-blasts-uncle-over-military-disrespect/articleshow/113047652.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113047652.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普的侄子弗雷德·特朗普三世在MSNBC的“最后期限：白宫”节目中批评他的叔叔对军队缺乏同情心。他强调了特朗普过去关于已故参议员约翰·麦凯恩的言论，并表示特朗普对武装部队的冷漠是真诚的、根深蒂固的，是出于自身利益的驱动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 02:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/doesnt-give-a-st-about-them-donald-trumps-nephew-fred-trump-blasts-uncle-over-military-disrespect/articleshow/113047652.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>